description:
E-Summit IIT Roorkee, in association with Divami Design Labs brings to you the Design Case Challenge - Obstacles to opportunities

Embark on an exciting journey of designing solutions from scratch based on problem statements from real-world dilemmas with a healthy dose of competition and attractive rewards!

Do you have what it takes to raise the bar?
card_description: Brainstorm your way through of mind-boggling problem statements based on real-world dilemmas to ideate, innovate and present a creative, practical and sustainable solution.
